Source: live-neverputt
Section: games
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Ronny Standtke <ronny.standtke@fhnw.ch>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: live-neverputt
Architecture: all
Depends: neverputt, live-resolution
Description: Starts neverputt with the current screen resolution
 This package enforces neverputt to start with the current screen resolution
 instead of the configured value. This way neverputt can easily be used on
 live systems without reconfiguration before every start.
